  "text": "Our observations of the effects of blocking inhibition within the preBö tC confirmed that the preBö tC can generate rhythmic inspiratory bursts in the absence of postsynaptic inhibition [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . However, inhibition modulates both respiratory rhythm and pattern in several ways.",
